Symbol.Script_3D:
! Plan Drawers
unID = 1
IF not(gs_shadow) THEN SHADOW OFF
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 then end if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 then resol 5 endif
resol gs_resol pen gs_cont_pen
add 0.02,0.02,0 MATERIAL toe_mat BLOCK A-0.04,B-0.02,toe_h gosub 2000 del 1
rotx 90 addy toe_h addz -B MATERIAL gs_cabinet_mat PRISM_ 10, B, 0,0,15, 0,ZZYZX-toe_h,15, A,ZZYZX-toe_h,15, A,0,15, 0,0,-1, 0.02,0.02,15, 0.02,ZZYZX-toe_h-0.02,15, A-0.02,ZZYZX-toe_h-0.02,15, A-0.02,0.02,15, 0.02,0.02,-1
gosub 3000
addx 0.02 addy 0.02 BLOCK A-0.04,ZZYZX-toe_h-0.04,0.02 del 5
add 0.02,0,toe_h+0.02
For j=1 to drawer_num MATERIAL gs_drawer_mat if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 & gs_bevel then addy 0.02 rotx 90 fprism_ gs_drawer_mat, gs_drawer_mat, gs_drawer_mat, gs_drawer_mat, 5, 0.02, 45, 0.01, 0, 0, 15, A-0.04, 0, 15, A-0.04, (ZZYZX-0.04-toe_h)/drawer_num-0.005, 15, 0, (ZZYZX-0.04-toe_h)/drawer_num-0.005, 15, 0, 0, -1 del 2 if j = 1 then addy 0.02 block A-0.04, B-0.04, ZZYZX-0.04-toe_h del 1 endif else block A-0.04,B-0.02,(ZZYZX-0.04-toe_h)/drawer_num-0.005 endif
if nDrawerKnob = 2 then for hi = 1 to 2 add knob_pl_x, 0, (ZZYZX-0.04-toe_h)/drawer_num/2 + knob_pl_y gosub 6000 del 1
mulx -1 addx -A + 0.04 next hi del 4 else add knob_pl_x + A/2 - 0.02, 0, (ZZYZX-0.04-toe_h)/drawer_num/2 + knob_pl_y gosub 6000 del 1 endif
addz (ZZYZX-0.04-toe_h)/drawer_num next j
gosub 2000
del drawer_num del 1
END
1000: roty 90 gosub 5000 del 1 return
2000: gosub 5000 return
3000: rotz 90 gosub 5000 del 1 return
5000:
vert 0, 0, 0 vert 1, 0, 0 vert 0, 1, 0 vert 0, 0, 1
coor 2, -1, -2, -3, -4
base
body -1
return
6000: if gs_knob_type_m >= 4 then if gs_knob_type_m <> 8 then roty 90 else roty -90 endif addz knob_size/2 endif
CALL "fa_knobtyp" parameters gs_detlevel_3D_m = gs_detlevel_3D_m, gs_knob_type_m = gs_knob_type_m, knob_size = knob_size, gs_resol = gs_resol, gs_shadow = gs_shadow, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, gs_knob_mat = gs_knob_mat
if gs_knob_type_m >= 4 then del 2
addz -knob_pl_y hotspot 0, 0, 0, unID, knob_pl_y, 1+128 : unID = unID + 1 hotspot 0, 0, -1, unID, knob_pl_y, 3+128 : unID = unID + 1 hotspot 0, 0, knob_pl_y, unID, knob_pl_y, 2 : unID = unID + 1 del 1 addx -knob_pl_x hotspot 0, 0, 0, unID, knob_pl_x, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot -1, 0, 0, unID, knob_pl_x, 3+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot knob_pl_x, 0, 0, unID, knob_pl_x, 2 : unID=unID+1 del 1
return
Symbol.Script_2D:
!! Plan Drawers.gsm call "fa_minimalspace" parameters all MSType = 1, unID = 3000
pen gs_cont_pen
unID = 1 HOTSPOT2 0, b, unID : unID = unID + 1 HOTSPOT2 a/2, b, unID : unID = unID + 1 HOTSPOT2 a/2, b/2, unID : unID = unID + 1
fill gs_fill_type
poly2_b 5,7,gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0,0,1, a,0,1, a,b,1, 0,b,1, 0,0,-1
CALL "Resize_A_B_ZZYZX" Parameters ALL
Symbol.Script_VL:
call "FM_types" parameters all
IF gs_cont_pen=0 THEN PARAMETERS gs_cont_pen=7 IF gs_fill_pen=0 THEN PARAMETERS gs_fill_pen=91
VALUES "a" RANGE [0.3,) VALUES "b" RANGE [0.2,) VALUES "zzyzx" RANGE [toe_h+0.05,)
VALUES "gs_detlevel_3D" `Detailed`,`Simple`,`Off` VALUES "gs_detlevel_3D_m" 0, 1, 2
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "gs_detlevel_3D" then if gs_detlevel_3D = `Off` then parameters gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 if gs_detlevel_3D = `Simple` then parameters gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 if gs_detlevel_3D = `Detailed` then parameters gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 else if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 then parameters gs_detlevel_3D = `Off` if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 then parameters gs_detlevel_3D = `Simple` if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 then parameters gs_detlevel_3D = `Detailed` endif
VALUES "gs_resol" RANGE [3,)
VALUES "drawer_num" RANGE [0,) VALUES "toe_h" RANGE [0,)
IF drawer_num = 0 THEN HIDEPARAMETER "gs_drawer_mat", "gs_knob_mat" IF abs(toe_h) < EPS THEN HIDEPARAMETER "toe_mat"
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 or gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN LOCK "gs_knob_mat" LOCK "gs_shadow", "gs_resol" ENDIF
dim st_knobtypes[9] st_knobtypes[1]=`None` st_knobtypes[2]=`Style 1` st_knobtypes[3]=`Style 2` st_knobtypes[4]=`Style 3` st_knobtypes[5]=`Style 4` st_knobtypes[6]=`Style 5` st_knobtypes[7]=`Style 6` st_knobtypes[8]=`Style 7` st_knobtypes[9]=`Style 8`
values "gs_knob_type_m" 0,1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8 values "gs_knob_type" st_knobtypes
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "gs_knob_type" then for iKnob = 1 to 9 if gs_knob_type = st_knobtypes[iKnob] then gs_knob_type_m = iKnob - 1 endif next iKnob parameters gs_knob_type_m = gs_knob_type_m else gs_knob_type = st_knobtypes[gs_knob_type_m+1] parameters gs_knob_type = gs_knob_type endif
values{2} "gs_knob_p_m" 1, `Horizontal`
lock "gs_knob_p_m"
values "knob_size" range [0.045,)
if gs_knob_type_m < 4 then lock "knob_size"
xKnobPosMod = 0
if gs_knob_type_m >= 4 then xKnobPosMod = knob_size/2
values "nDrawerKnob" 1, 2 if nDrawerKnob = 2 then values "knob_pl_x" range [0.02 + xKnobPosMod, A/2 - 0.04 - xKnobPosMod] else values "knob_pl_x" range [-A/2 + 0.02 + xKnobPosMod, A/2 - 0.02 - xKnobPosMod] endif
values "knob_pl_y" range [-((ZZYZX-0.04-toe_h)/drawer_num/2) + 0.02, ((ZZYZX-0.04-toe_h)/drawer_num/2) - 0.02]
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "nDrawerKnob" then if nDrawerKnob = 1 then knob_pl_x = 0 else knob_pl_x = 0.1 endif parameters knob_pl_x = knob_pl_x endif
if gs_knob_type_m = 0 then lock "gs_knob_type_m", "gs_knob_p_m", "knob_size", "knob_pl_x", "knob_pl_y", "gs_knob_mat" hideparameter "gs_knob_type_m", "gs_knob_p_m", "knob_size", "knob_pl_x", "knob_pl_y", "gs_knob_mat" endif
Symbol.Script_UI:
ui_page 1
x2TextPos = 200 x3TextPos = 355 y2TextPos = 40 xPictPos = 30 yPictPos = 60 length2Text = 150 length3Text = 89 yPictDist = 115 dy = 25
bHideXDrawerKnobPos = 0 if gs_knob_type_m = 0 then bHideXDrawerKnobPos = 1 bHideZDrawerKnobPos = 0 if gs_knob_type_m = 0 then bHideZDrawerKnobPos = 1 bHideDrawerKnobPos = 1 bHideDrawerKnobSize = 0 if gs_knob_type_m < 4 then bHideDrawerKnobSize = 1 bHideMatDrawerKnob = 0 if gs_knob_type_m = 0 then bHideMatDrawerKnob = 1 bHideDrawerKnobNum = 0 if gs_knob_type_m = 0 then bHideDrawerKnobNum = 1
ui_infield{3} "gs_knob_type", xPictPos, yPictPos, 130, 85, 2, "Knob_Types_N(13)", 12, 4, 130, 85, 60, 80, 1,`Style 1`,`Style 1`, 2,`Style 2`,`Style 2`, 3,`Style 3`,`Style 3`, 4,`Style 4`,`Style 4`, 5,`Style 5`,`Style 5`, 6,`Style 6`,`Style 6`, 7,`Style 7`,`Style 7`, 8,`Style 8`,`Style 8`, 9,`None`,`None`
ui_style 0,1 ui_outfield `Knob`, 12, 20, 120, 13 ui_style 0,0
y = 0
ui_outfield `Horizontal Position`, x2TextPos, y2TextPos, length2Text, 18, 4 * bHideXDrawerKnobPos ui_infield "knob_pl_x", x3TextPos, y2TextPos, length3Text, 19
y = y + dy
ui_outfield `Vertical Position`, x2TextPos, y2TextPos + y, length2Text, 18, 4 * bHideZDrawerKnobPos ui_infield "knob_pl_y", x3TextPos, y2TextPos + y, length3Text, 19
y = y + dy
ui_outfield `Placing`, x2TextPos, y2TextPos + y, length2Text, 18, 4 * bHideDrawerKnobPos ui_infield{3} "gs_knob_p_m", x3TextPos, y2TextPos + y, length3Text, 19
y = y + dy
ui_outfield `Size`, x2TextPos, y2TextPos + y, length2Text, 18, 4 * bHideDrawerKnobSize ui_infield "knob_size", x3TextPos, y2TextPos + y, length3Text, 19
y = y + dy
stDNum1 = "1" stDNum2 = "2"
ui_outfield `No. of Knobs by Drawer`, x2TextPos, y2TextPos + y, length2Text, 18, 4 * bHideDrawerKnobNum ui_infield{3} "nDrawerKnob", x3TextPos, y2TextPos + y, length3Text-18, 19, 8, "", 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, stDNum1, 1, 0, stDNum2, 2
y = y + dy
ui_outfield `Surface`, x2TextPos, y2TextPos + y, length2Text, 18, 4 * bHideMatDrawerKnob ui_infield "gs_knob_mat", x3TextPos, y2TextPos + y, length3Text, 22
